*Ljude* su često zbunjeni problemima koji se pojavljuju u njihovim životima. (People are often confused by the problems that arise in their lives.)

Mnogi *ljudi* se bore da prežive na dnevnom nivou. (Many people struggle to survive on a daily basis.)

Danas se očekuje da *ljudima* bude dostupno širok spektar raznolikosti. (Today people are expected to have access to a wide range of diversity.)

U kulturama širom sveta postoje različiti načini na koje *ljudi* mogu da se identifikuju. (In cultures around the world, there are different ways for people to identify themselves.)

U narodu će uvek biti onih kojima je potrebna pomoć *ljudi* iz okoline. (In the community there will always be those who need help from people around them.)